</title>
<subSubSection id="D9129AD126C6025D6D9DF581042D6E19" pageId="null" pageNumber="790" type="description">
<paragraph id="7DFBEEAE0F6C50959BC4DBCA3231EC26" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">
Unterscheidet sich von der Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="E83E711620B386A8352E8760AF596164" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Gypsophila" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="790" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6E53E35FFE706020D06B6A44F284EFA7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">Gypsophila</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 787) durch folgende Merkmale: Kelch 
<normalizedToken id="32AD76344B8BEC1D864773DD8E4AD004" originalValue="röhrenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">roehrenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="9FA6AA701F8F51254675FF64C0DB41C8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">
15-25nervig, ohne 
<normalizedToken id="86D4C97FBFBD566DDF01D93ADD119B06" originalValue="trockenhäutige" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">trockenhaeutige</normalizedToken>
Streifen; 
<normalizedToken id="6C4EE1B94D547AE0DFD06BC660175408" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
am Schlundeingang mit 2teiliger Schuppe
</emphasis>
(Nebenkrone).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="31DE9D4AD8177642A2ADF289D82FFF3C" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">
Die Gattung 
<emphasis id="2942BC9169365D2F87B8E871FA86FF61" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">
<taxonomicName id="8FF0771F282744E9E542C4AD671F7618" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Saponaria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="790" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Saponaria</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="99F3889FB021301941567F88A337551E" originalValue="umfaβt" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">umfaβt</normalizedToken>
etwa 30 vorwiegend mediterrane Arten. Chromosomengrundzahl
</emphasis>
n = 14.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7CE839690A2C42042A8046FCC3BAB4C2" pageId="null" pageNumber="790">
<table id="5F24448A8515B1E16C9E411E1AA59275" frame="void" pageId="null" pageNumber="790" rules="none" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
